            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-f91c59cb-c349-4ad3-911f-1dc56e01663c">
                Major Hills
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f91c59cb-c349-4ad3-911f-1dc56e01663c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-02-14/debates/e9a26890-093f-465b-aba5-8015823fc78d/ForeignLoans(BritishBondholders)#contribution-f91c59cb-c349-4ad3-911f-1dc56e01663c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister whether the attention of His Majesty's Government has been called to the heavy losses to investors, to the revenue, and to this country as a whole which are involved by defaults on foreign loans owned by bondholders in this country; and what action His Majesty's Government have taken or propose to take to protect the interests of bondholders in such cases?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f91c59cb-c349-4ad3-911f-1dc56e01663c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-02-14/debates/e9a26890-093f-465b-aba5-8015823fc78d/ForeignLoans(BritishBondholders)#contribution-f91c59cb-c349-4ad3-911f-1dc56e01663c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
